  p My dad runs a small!{' '}
    a(href="https://www.maximizeyourpotential.co.uk/" target="_blank") study skills company
    |!{' '}in the UK.
  //- p Up until last year the only marketing they did was sending flyers to schools — their target market. But, over time, flyers had lost their effectiveness, so my dad started thinking about running digital ads.
  p It's an old school business. Up until last year the only marketing he's ever done was sending flyers to schools. But, flyers had stopped working so well, so he started thinking about running digital ads.
